{"tid":493296,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"韓狗：應該由允兒演花木蘭","createTime":"2017-12-08T11:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T11:07:58.000Z","uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"980f42e51681c5f09b4a9b13187ea395ab8c3513","tid":493296,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:07:58.000Z","msg":"韓國網友先是推薦林允兒出演花木蘭，然後又物色了崔始源當男主角。這本來就是中國人的故事，他們這麼熱情乾嘛?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/190713_15601d438a9059efb98a225d6baa7a33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F190713_15601d438a9059efb98a225d6baa7a33.jpg&h=c98141af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/190640_afed8bc5e8d59a8acb536023a743077e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F190640_afed8bc5e8d59a8acb536023a743077e.jpg&h=884514a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/190640_8acfd305fe2dbb86b8c8f7b3286c148a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F190640_8acfd305fe2dbb86b8c8f7b3286c148a.jpg&h=d6eb9a4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/190641_8acfd305fe2dbb86b8c8f7b3286c148a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F190641_8acfd305fe2dbb86b8c8f7b3286c148a.jpg&h=3efc0aea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/190641_5d4f4d5bff143170cf91ac354d0c38d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F190641_5d4f4d5bff143170cf91ac354d0c38d0.jpg&h=7400bdf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有點不太理解這位韓國網友的評論:花木蘭還是叫中國人演了，好想哭哦。<br />\n<br />\n韓國真是對中國文化有著蜜汁執著啊。全世界誰不知道花木蘭是中國的。<br />\n<br />\n花木蘭是中國南北朝時期的古代民族英雄，最早出現在當時的一首敘事詩《木蘭辭》中。連1998年的動畫版《花木蘭》，是迪士尼根據這首詩改編出來的。<br />\n<br />\n如果要拍真人版，難道不是中國女演員更適合?"}]}